    • Uses of VisualizeImageLabelsRequest in com.gisfederal.gpudb

      Methods in com.gisfederal.gpudb with parameters of type VisualizeImageLabelsRequest 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      VisualizeImageLabelsResponse GPUdb.visualizeImageLabels(VisualizeImageLabelsRequest request)
      Generates a rasterized image tile containing text labels defined by data contained in the given table, suitable for overlaying onto a feature image tile covering the same area (for example one generated using GPUdb.visualizeImage(VisualizeImageRequest)).
